<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0740a17shiYuanHao"><lb
ed="T" n="0740a17"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0740a17"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000009882">蘇州開元寺</placeName><persName key="A009613">元浩</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0740a18"/><persName key="A009613">釋元浩</persName>，姓秦氏，字<persName key="A009613">廣成</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳門</placeName>人也。綺歲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g882"/>依<lb
ed="T" n="0740a19"/><placeName key="PL000000009362">晉陵靈山寺</placeName><persName key="A009622">慧日禪師</persName>出家，具滿律戒，配<lb
ed="T" n="0740a20"/>本州<placeName key="PL000000009853">龍興寺</placeName>，尋為<placeName key="PL000000009470">荊溪</placeName><persName key="A001307">湛然<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>囑累弟子。<lb
ed="T" n="0740a21"/>初受《法華》、《止觀》，已得醍醐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g883"/>，唯以裂大網、感<lb
ed="T" n="0740a22"/>大果、成大行、歸大處以為大願。宴居<ptr type="glossary" target="#g884"/>三<lb
ed="T" n="0740a23"/>昧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g178"/>，常隨佛後，希夷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g885"/>自得，人莫能知。其祕密<lb
ed="T" n="0740a24"/>深遠如海印三昧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g886"/>，不言出處，常行佛事。與<lb
ed="T" n="0740a25"/>夫難行苦行，更相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g887"/>祖述<ptr type="glossary" target="#g889"/>，默傳心要；為論為<lb
ed="T" n="0740a26"/>記、靈芝瑞草，以為功德。傳於後世者，不同<lb
ed="T" n="0740a27"/>日而語矣。<persName key="A009613">浩</persName>注解《大涅槃經》，為文首序，德<lb
ed="T" n="0740a28"/>美圓實，志願顯現。蓋錄其所證之意，而見于<lb
ed="T" n="0740a29"/>文，曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009613">余</ref>聞先覺之大寶曰『常』<ptr target="#n890"/>，在宥<ptr target="#n891"/>布和之盛<pb ed="T" n="0740b" xml:id="T50.2061.0740b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0740b01"/>典曰『教』，率土知化之歸<anchor xml:id="beg0740sgsz1"/>宗<anchor xml:id="end0740sgsz1"/>曰『行』，交感人心<lb
ed="T" n="0740b02"/>之至極曰『證』，然則以<anchor xml:id="beg0740sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>道御</sic><corr>道行御其</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0740sgsz2"/>時，以法性合其<lb
ed="T" n="0740b03"/>運，當應物之際，與顯晦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g892"/>同其光，恢張至<lb
ed="T" n="0740b04"/>化而自他昭著者，實播於鴻名。欽恭聞思，協<lb
ed="T" n="0740b05"/>和至極，四德<ptr type="glossary" target="#g893"/>克彰者，實存乎妙體。格變群<lb
ed="T" n="0740b06"/>家，歷觀諸行，至典克修，庶績有成者，實賴<lb
ed="T" n="0740b07"/>乎宗本。信以授人，大明宗極，敷暢厥旨，庶<lb
ed="T" n="0740b08"/>幾有補於將來者，實存乎妙用。博綜群言<lb
ed="T" n="0740b09"/>以立誠訓，風行十方率用歸順者，實存乎<lb
ed="T" n="0740b10"/>妙教矣。」此<persName key="A009613">浩</persName>之法要，如<persName key="A002424">王輔嗣</persName>之法〈繫辭〉<ptr target="#n894"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0740b11"/><persName key="A004022">司馬遷</persName>之〈自敘〉<ptr target="#n895"/>，<persName key="A009619">管仲</persName>能言〈輕重〉<ptr target="#n896"/>，<persName key="A004486">孟子</persName>之傳《春<lb
ed="T" n="0740b12"/>秋》，雖儒、釋不同，其義一也。以<date key="j20198232019823" when-iso="+0817-12-26"><name>元和</name>十二年<lb
ed="T" n="0740b13"/>十一月十一日</date>示疾，右脇累足，入于涅槃，<lb
ed="T" n="0740b14"/>非二乘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g724"/>境界，真如來定也。<date key="j20201802020180" when-iso="+0818-12-18">明年十一月十三<lb
ed="T" n="0740b15"/>日</date>闍維，起塔於<placeName key="PL000000010007">蘇州西北虎丘東山</placeName>南原也。<lb
ed="T" n="0740b16"/><persName key="A009613">浩</persName>耽學味道，不涉餘事，常隨<persName key="A001307">然師</persName>聽其言<lb
ed="T" n="0740b17"/>說，曾無倦色。分析義理，派流川注，必默記<lb
ed="T" n="0740b18"/>而暗誦，一言不失。數年之後，人始知之。<persName key="A001307">然<lb
ed="T" n="0740b19"/>師</persName>曰：「<persName key="A002780">回</persName>也如愚<ptr target="#n897"/>」罕為人說，多辭以不能，及<lb
ed="T" n="0740b20"/>被<persName key="A001081">梁</persName>、<persName key="A009637">田</persName>二君苦勸請之，始著《涅槃經解述》。<lb
ed="T" n="0740b21"/><persName key="A009613">浩</persName>與<placeName key="PL000000042591">上都雲華寺</placeName><persName key="A001755">華嚴澄觀<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>，若孔門之<lb
ed="T" n="0740b22"/><persName key="A021880">游</persName>、<persName key="A010088">夏</persName>焉<ptr target="#n797"/>。其儒流受業，翰林學士<persName key="A001081">梁<roleName>公</roleName>肅</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000009928">蘇州<lb
ed="T" n="0740b23"/></placeName>刺史<persName key="A009637">田<roleName>公</roleName>敦</persName>。緇流受業者，<persName key="A009639">智恒</persName>、<persName key="A009640">子瑜</persName>、<persName key="A009643">道儒</persName>、<persName key="A009644">仲<lb
ed="T" n="0740b24"/>儀</persName>、<persName key="A009645">仲良</persName>五人，持經講論，傳之無窮。大比丘尼<lb
ed="T" n="0740b25"/><persName key="A009646">識微</persName>、<persName key="A009647">道巽</persName>、<persName key="A009648">志真</persName>、<persName key="A009649">悟極</persName>，此四人者高潔之倫，深<lb
ed="T" n="0740b26"/>練禪觀。初<persName key="A009613">浩</persName>為<ref type="person" target="#A001081 #A009637">二官</ref>所請注經，預夢甚為<lb
ed="T" n="0740b27"/>奇特。又庭階生花，非人間恒所見者。祥鳥<lb
ed="T" n="0740b28"/>飛馴，五彩絕異。刺史<persName key="A009650">崔恭</persName>撰塔碑<ptr target="#n898"/>，立于<placeName key="PL000000010031">虎丘<lb
ed="T" n="0740b29"/>山羅漢石壇</placeName>之左。後有<persName key="A009651">行滿</persName>、<persName key="A001552">道暹</persName>、<persName key="A000673">明曠</persName>皆著<pb ed="T" n="0740c" xml:id="T50.2061.0740c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0740c01"/>述，廣天台之道歟。</p>    
